    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Common liquid secondary alcohol, and the first commercial synthetic alcohol. Synthesized by the hydration of propylene. Frequently used as an antiseptic, and in cosmetics. In industry it is used as a solvent and to produce acetone.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
